\frac{1}{2*5}+\frac{1}{3*6}+\frac{1}{4*7}+...+\frac{1}{(n-2)(n+1)}+\frac{1}{(n-1)(n+2)}  
n's
i's
i
\frac{n(n+1)}{2}
\sum_{i=1}^n \frac{1}{(i-2)(i+1)}+\frac{1}{(i-1)(i+2)}  
 \frac{1}{2*5} + \cdots + \frac{1}{(n-1)(n+2)} =\sum_{i = 3} ^n \frac{1}{(i-1)(i+2)} 
\frac{1}{i-1} - \frac{1}{i+2} = \frac{i+2 - (i-1)}{(i-1)(i+2)} = 3 \frac{1}{(i-1)(i+2)}
 \sum_{i = 3} ^n \frac{1}{(i-1)(i+2)} = \sum_{i = 3} ^n \frac{1}{3} \left( \frac{1}{i-1} - \frac{1}{i+2} \right) = \frac{1}{3} \sum_{i = 3} ^n \left( \frac{1}{i-1} - \frac{1}{i+2} \right).  
\frac1{(i-2)(i+1)}=\frac13\cdot\frac{i+1-(i-2)}{(i-2)(i+1)}=\frac13\left(\frac1{i-2}-\frac1{i+1}\right)
\frac1{(i-1)(i+2)}=\cdots=\frac13\left(\frac1{i-1}-\frac1{i+2}\right)
i=1,2,\cdots,n-1,n
